\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No, we didn't that 
was just that. I can tell you right start the old farmer what I worked for he said a man carry a sack of wheat home on his back every Saturday night was thirteen shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And was there no other kind of employment open to you if you had wanted another kind of job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
No, that wasn't until some years. And on that same farm I was put with a pair of horses - I done anything before then but when I was put with a pair of horses when I was about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 17}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  and I was them }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Was that driving them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, I used to plough and do anything on the farm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Tell me about when you first started, Did you know the people you were working with.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid91116\charrsid11799661  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 You said there was another man as well and you had to lead the horses - the front horse.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, about that they used to have these }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
