 and I used to have the one in front and lead it, and then there was another fellow to help me there was another man behind this drill to see after the machine. So there was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  men and a lad with this drill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And the other man who worked with your father had you known him before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 So when you took your first job you didn't meet strangers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh no, no, no, no, that was me grandfather
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 So it was the grandfather, the father and the son.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No - the grandfather was my mother's father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And were there any other people you met at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh yes there was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  of us - there was a stockman and a shepherd and what they called 
a dayman - used to do just anything, oh yes there was yes - and all the summer time we when the time come we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 and getting the crops ready for another year that was our business that was real land work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Did you all sit and have your lunch together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
No, some of us used to go home same as at breakfast we used to have together but same as at dinner time close to home which sometimes we were we used to go home to dinner, see - that's how we done it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 When you said you had bread and cheese and tea did you call that your breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No, that was our lunch }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 11}}}11}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  o'clock{\*\xmlclose}. We had breakfast, lunch and then at }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  we used to have just a little piece and then we went till }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 5}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  and then we had our cooked supper, when we got home you see - that's how we done it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 It's interesting what people called the meals in those days. You called it lunch that meal that you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 11}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
 o'clock and then at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  we used to go just home and as I said we were back again at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
