\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  till nearly }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  and then from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  till nearly }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 4}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 .
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid1199167 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
You'd go both times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Both times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And what sort of a service would it be at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 10}}}10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  o'clock{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 There used to be a Sunday school before the service and there used 
to be a preacher service and we used to go to Sunday school again in the afternoon and there was a preaching service in the afternoon wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And how old were you when you stopped going to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Well, let me see. About }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 40}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 About }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 40}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
! Oh, I see. Sunday school wasn't just for children then.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  I'll be right plain. I was a teacher in the Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 So when you stopped being a pupil you became a teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 How old were you when you started teaching then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 12 or 13}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, I loved it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Both as a pupil and as a teacher?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. And there's one thing their mother used to make all their own bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 What days did she bake?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mr. J. Saturday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And what kind of bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh beautiful. Better than it is to? Day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Was it the white flour or the wholemeal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, white flour. But what mother used to do - she'd bake it the last Saturday and we'd begin that bread next Saturday. That's a week old.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Why did she do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Well it was better?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 In what way was it better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Well, it seemed to taste sweeter
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Did she store it somewhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh yes. She used to have a big pan to put it in. With a lid or not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes with a lid.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And would she bake anything else with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 If we'd got any fruit and the like she'd bake our fruit pies and that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And would she also keep them or did you eat those.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 We used to eat them on a Sunday? That' was Sunday dinner
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And did she bake any cake?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes sometimes. She used to bake what they call shortcake with use a little sugar in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Flour and sugar and anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And a little fat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J.: made off the bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mr. J. made off the bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Did your sisters help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh yes they used to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 What sort of jobs did they do in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
Oh they used to do the housework. Dust and sweeping up and all such things as them. They used to do a bit of needlework and crocheting. All such things as them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And did they do any sending?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, yes (laughter)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And did they do any washing
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 I don't think my sisters did. Mother used to. She used to wash for all of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And how often would she wash.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 One day a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 A set day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, a set day wash. She'd be washing all day. It would take the whole day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 She'd start about when in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 8 or 9}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And what did she wash in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 She had a wooden tub after the job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Can you describe it to me. What sort of shape was it. It was round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 A round tub as round as that table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And what sort of size? Big as the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, no, no, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Half the size?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 It would be about that width across.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 What sort of soap did she have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Sunlight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Did she have hot water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 In the copper. She'd boil the clothes in the copper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 After she'd washed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And what about the rinsing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 She used to do that in a tub after she'd washed. Put some more water in you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 What room in the house would she do it in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 The kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 After she had done that how would she get the clothes wrung out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 She used to wring it herself and then hung them on the line to dry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And suppose it rained?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 She'd bring them in and hung them out the next day if it was a drying day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And suppose there was a real bad spell of weather. How would she get them dry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 She used to hang them up indoors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And did she iron?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh yes, she used to iron.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 When would she iron?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 She used to have certain times and she used to use these old iron flats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. Box irons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, she used to use the box irons and then she used to use what they call flats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 What is a box iron?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 I wish}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  I'd got one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mr. J. So do I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
Mrs. J. They were asking for one not long ago. We had one, my sister had one with a brass face - lovely! No electric. You heat them in a fire, take the tongs. Drop that one out, drop the other one in and use it long as you could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Then drop that one out and use another hot one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh I see. You put the heated piece inside the iron.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And what was it itself, this piece.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mr. J. Iron.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 The piece itself - did it have a name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 You'd call it a heater.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 The other kind how would you heat that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Real flat with a handle on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And how would you heat that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Sit that in front of the fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. on a trivet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And would she iron on the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, there were no ironing boards them days. Mrs. J: She'd got an ironing blanket - a sheet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Can you tell me more about Sunday School and the life at the chapel? Were there a lot of people who used to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 How many for example in your Sunday School when you were about 13 or 14?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 About 70.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 All in one room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes all in one room. There were different classes and different teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 How many teachers for example would there be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  or }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 .
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 When you started you had how many in your class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Was there any social life and community around the chapel. Or did you just meet there on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 We just met there on the Sundays, didn't we?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Did you get to know people that you might not have known before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, meet people, yes! That was a regular happy place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 That was a happy place. There'd be as many as }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 40 or 50}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  there at the services Sundays mornings. Happy times. Yes, they were. Mrs. J. Then we'd have what they call an anniversary.
 All the children used to learn a recitation or a dialogue - you know what a dialogue is - talking one to the other }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  or }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  of them and all - tremendous. Wonderful times!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 How often were the anniversaries?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Once a year. Whitsunday
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 In some parts of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}England{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 everybody gets clothes at Whitsunday. Did they round here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Can you remember anything you did at the anniversaries?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Course! Sakes alive yes! I can! The recitations I used to learn and say, get up and say in front of the people it was a regular thing.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 One, or more than one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes, I used to say \'85 We used to have }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  services that day. I used to do}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661  o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 ne in afternoon}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6565851\charrsid11799661 ,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  one at night and I used to go up to the old teacher, she was a good old lady. She used to come to me, she
 say Bob, she say 'Can't you learn this? I used to say, 'I dare say I can'. I used to learn it. Yes. That was happy times, we liked to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Were they long, the recitations. Can you remember one that you can perhaps say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 Good gracious}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  alive. I 
can't remember what I learned there but I've learned a lot since you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. He's gone out reciting.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 I've gone out to recite different places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. He's gone to the old people's home. He used to go there to give a recitation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 You still do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No, I haven't gone there late while. I'm eighty-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  and I'm getting past it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 But you did them for many years did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes from the time I was a child up till now lately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 You say you don't remember the ones you learned when you were in your teens. You can't even remember the name of one?
