\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No. We used to see - we'd be out Sundays so we'll come so-and so's and we'd do it. That's how we used to do it.
