\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Sankey's hymns.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes that's what we used to play. And of course we used to have a hymn book over h
ere. We used to play out of the hymn book. That's what we used to get our hymns from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 Moodie and Sankey.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
