and Sankey and the hymn book, wasn't it.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And when you played did you sometimes just have the tune or did you have singing as well.
