\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, I see. Mrs. J. Both went to Ardleigh School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 But it was when you met at the church you decided to start \'85.
