August. Mrs. J. Seems wonderful when we look back and think about things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 So after you met at the church you started walking out the next day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And how long before you decided to get married? Mrs. J. We were walking out together, how long? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2128075\charrsid11799661 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2128075\charrsid11799661 10 or 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. You couldn't save the money. You couldn't get married as a lot of them will }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 to'day}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 . They have everything they want but they can't pay for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 We had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
 room cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mr. J. We had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  room cottage and I'll surely tell you we paid for everything when we had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. We'd got a little nest egg to go on with. A very quiet life but we've had all we wanted in a reasonable way, haven't we?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mr. J. Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes. Mrs. J. We've never }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 
quarrelled}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 . An argument sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Self: An argument doesn't do any harm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Mrs. J. Does you good!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 When you met your wife at this wedding. Did you suggest to her that you go out the next day or how was it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 That's like th
is. We talked things over. And when we first went together we hadn't got the money to get married. And her father and mother they were afflicted for years. And we made up our minds that we wouldn't get married till they passed over. That's how that was an
d they passed over at the Christmas and we got married the next June so we lived in the house that they lived in. That's how that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And after those }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2128075\charrsid11799661 10 or 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  years how often would you spend time together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Would you see her say every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 
No, not every day, because she's out at service. She's in service the fore part of the time we went together. And I used to bike up and see her every thought one weekend I had. Sometimes she'd come home the afternoon I used to go home 
with her. Or she'd go home for Sunday. But the latter part of the time she lived at home. Looking after her people you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 When she was in service where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Colchester. And some of the time she lived across here at Nicholls's. And some of the time at Little Bromley Hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Did you say some of the time she was at Nicholls's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Some of the time she was at Mr. Nicholls's. And her last place was Little Bromley Hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 How many years was she there?
