\insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 . So when you got married you would have been how old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 About }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2128075\charrsid11799661 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid91116\charrsid11799661 4}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661  I reckon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 And did the time seen to pass very slowly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No! no. I used to go and see her week nights and we used to have the evening together. Then Sundays she'd come
 home. I used to live next door to her. I used to see her home and that like and course she used to write and I used to write to her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 How often would she write?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Oh, once a week.
