\insrsid7955298\charrsid11799661 24. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 I recollect that was all put on a blackboard what was there in the morning and what was there in the afternoon they were all counted up.
