\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 No the number what there was in the school.
