\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 He didn't he was..\'85 Yes\'85.. He was \'85.. I had a good father and a good mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Can you tell me anything about meal times? For example, when you used to come home and have your supper that was your main meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Was all the family together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3149352 RJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1199167 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1079458\charrsid11799661 Can you describe it to me where you'd sit and what you'd have to eat.
